name: 1 SEO Keyword Article
description:
All content is 100% original

You retain the rights to all material.

Articles are between 350-500 words and have a standard keyword density of about 3%.

When you are checking out there will be a section entitled "Keywords and Instructions" where you can enter the keywords that you want used in your articles. If you don't know specific keywords just put in a general description of what you're looking for. I will email you if I have questions.

I will email you when I receive you order to clarify keywords and give you an estimated date of delivery. Depending on how many project I have delivery could take up to two weeks although most of the time projects are turned around in a week or less.

** Please note this does NOT include submission service. If you want your articles submitted to the three largest article directories you can purchase articles with submission service in another listing**

name: Submission Service
description:
Buy this service with any article or article set and your article(s) will be submitted to ezinearticles, iSnare and ArticleMarketer. Those are the three biggest article distribution sites on the Net and can bring in lots of hits to your website plus give you very important inbound anchor text links. 

It may take anywhere from 3 days to 2 weeks to get the articles approved and published. You'll receive a link via email to each live article once it's published.
